{"tid":2364450,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 黎巴嫩沙威瑪烤雞上腿 配 鮮乳酪青瓜忌廉汁 拼 甜粟米洋蔥炒著仔","createTime":"2021-01-13T04:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T09:58:42.000Z","uid":33359,"like":37,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"401382ea8369663e7838445e06360814e79c3eec","tid":2364450,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQo12mD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQo12mD.jpg&h=557cb280&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZSRE8v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZSRE8v.jpg&h=8267deeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞皮燒到好香脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞肉嫩滑得黎好重香料味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由其係孜然味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人幾鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n青瓜忌廉汁好清新解漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論係配雞肉配著仔都好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n炒著仔今次味道淡咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再咸返少少更好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個喉嚨好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5d934a9d58858feca6ebf439b1da7a82259363","tid":2364450,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:08:52.000Z","msg":"早食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3839d27c0d9644db61552f7249cb1c864a791d99","tid":2364450,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d